</tgroup>
</table>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V10A510047.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "21.261mm" ver = "02" gw = "39" gh = "44"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510318.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "129.783mm" ver = "01" gw = "127" gh = "351"/>
</figure>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
After applying ATF to cooler check valve (1) and spring (2), install them to transaxle case (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510319.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.297mm" ver = "01" gw = "148" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
After applying ATF to new governor No.1 gasket (1), install it to transaxle case.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510320.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.714mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "121"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install solenoid harness to transaxle case. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106024"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install manual valve rod (1) to manual valve lever (3) and then install valve body assembly (2) to transaxle case.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510322.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.624mm" ver = "01" gw = "166" gh = "112"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Tighten valve body bolts to specified torque, by referring to the following table and figure.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5A012">
<t-part>
Valve body bolt
</t-part>
<t-value1>
11
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
1.1
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
8.0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
